Rule #12: &ldquo;Learn foreign languages.&rdquo; 1
Learn at least one of the major ones such as French, German, Spanish. 2
 Originally created and published in Mar 2010 &#x21a9;&#xfe0e;
It depends on your country of origin, of course. For instance, for Russian native speakers, the list would be English, French, German. &#x21a9;&#xfe0e;
